&lt;p&gt;The morning the storm rolled through, I reached for a sleeve of hook and loop sanding discs that had sat overnight on the bench. The disc stack had a faint wave to it—just enough curl to feel wrong when I pinched the edges. A minute into the first pass on white oak, the orbit pattern started to chatter. The grit looked fine, but the face felt warmer than it should, and the pad sounded different—thinner, harsher. When I peeled the disc, the loops carried a trace of condensate and dust paste. Five more minutes and the edge was lifting under lateral load. The disc flew off.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/17.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/26/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/disc-storage-and-humidity-care-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Replace Discs Safely During Operation</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 09 Feb 2026 14:22:02 +0000</pubDate><category>Hook-and-Loop Discs</category><category>grit-240</category><category>grit progression</category><category>orbital sander</category><category>dust control</category><description>Learn how to change hook and loop sanding discs safely mid-project—avoid slips, protect your pad, and get cleaner, faster results with every grit.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="safe-swaps-for-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs"&gt;Safe Swaps for Hook and Loop Sanding Discs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The hum of the sander is oddly soothing until the disc starts to chatter and the finish turns patchy. You ease off the pressure, glance at the clock, and weigh a familiar trade-off: keep pushing a dull disc or risk a clumsy change that costs both time and surface quality. Maybe you’re refinishing a mid-century dresser you promised your sister, or you’re on the third room of a floor restoration where the deadline has more backbone than the old oak. Either way, the moments you swap abrasives can make or break a project. This is where hook and loop sanding discs quietly earn their keep—quick changes, consistent grip, and fewer interruptions when the job is in full swing.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/01.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/02/09/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/replace-discs-safely-during-operation-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Psa Versus Hook And Loop Disc Differences</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 21 Jan 2026 15:17:57 +0000</pubDate><category>Hook-and-Loop Discs</category><category>grit-360</category><description>Learn the real differences between PSA and hook &amp;amp; loop sanding discs, with pro tips on grip, heat, dust control, and finish—so you pick the right disc every</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="psa-vs-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs-explained"&gt;PSA vs hook and loop sanding discs explained&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first time I watched a sanding disc leave the pad at full RPM, it was a fresh cup of coffee and a maple tabletop on the line. I’d been stepping through grits—80, 120, 150—chasing that clean, even scratch pattern before dye. Then the shop warmed up, the workpiece warmed up, and my backing pad warmed up. Ten minutes later, the disc glazed, heat built, and off it went—cartwheeling into a cardboard box like a frisbee with a grudge. That day taught me that backing matters as much as grit. If you’ve ever fought adhesive smears from a PSA disc or melted hooks that won’t grip, you already know the stakes. The choice between PSA and hook and loop sanding discs isn’t academic; it’s about finish quality, workflow speed, and how many discs you burn through to get a surface you’re proud of.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/14.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/21/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/psa-versus-hook-and-loop-disc-differences-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>10</readingTime></item><item><title>Soft Interface Pad For Contour Sanding</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2026 13:38:32 +0000</pubDate><category>Hook-and-Loop Discs</category><category>grit-80</category><category>grit-100</category><category>grit-150</category><category>grit-180</category><category>grit-220</category><category>grit-240</category><category>grit-320</category><category>grit-400</category><category>grit-800</category><category>grit-1200</category><description>Engineer-tested guide to soft interface pads for contour sanding and hook and loop sanding discs—materials, heat control, dust, and real-world results.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="hook-and-loop-sanding-discs-and-soft-interface-pads"&gt;Hook and Loop Sanding Discs and Soft Interface Pads&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Early Sunday, the shop is quiet except for the soft thrum of a random-orbit sander. You’re easing into the inside radius of a chair arm, the kind of curve where the wood tells on you: one careless second and you’ve burned through stain on the edge. You swap to a softer setup—an interface pad between the pad and your hook and loop sanding discs—and the whole feel changes. The pad yields just enough to keep the abrasive in full contact along the curve, and the sander stops chattering. Your hands relax. The dust stream settles into the vacuum instead of fogging the bench light. The finish doesn’t scream for attention anymore; it whispers that you got the contour right.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/27.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/01/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/soft-interface-pad-for-contour-sanding-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Avoid Edge Lift At High Rpm</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 12 Dec 2025 13:40:36 +0000</pubDate><category>Hook-and-Loop Discs</category><category>grit-150</category><description>Prevent edge lift at high RPM with hook and loop sanding discs—optimize pads, pressure, heat, and workflow for flawless surface preparation.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="stop-edge-lift-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs-at-rpm"&gt;Stop Edge Lift: Hook and Loop Sanding Discs at RPM&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first time I heard the flit of a disc edge slapping a workpiece at full speed, I knew the surface was lost. The panel had been blocked flat, the vacuum switched on, and the sander wound up to max. Ten seconds later, the perimeter of the abrasive began to chatter. The hook field ran hot, the outer 5 mm lifted, and a spiral scar traced the grain like a tattoo I didn’t order. If you’ve ever watched your finish window close in a heartbeat, you know the feeling—time and material slipping away because the disc couldn’t hold together at speed.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/11.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/instagram/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/pinterest/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/12/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/cards/facebook/avoid-edge-lift-at-high-rpm-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Best Grits For Automotive Sanding Discs</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/26/best-grits-for-automotive-sanding-discs-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/26/best-grits-for-automotive-sanding-discs-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Nov 2025 14:17:48 +0000</pubDate><category>Hook-and-Loop Discs</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-360</category><category>dust control</category><description>Learn the best grits for automotive sanding discs, with precise workflows, abrasive choices, and pro tips for faster, flatter finishes using hook and loop</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="best-grits-for-automotive-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs"&gt;Best Grits for Automotive Hook and Loop Sanding Discs&lt;/h2&gt;
