y>grit-240</category><category>grit progression</category><description>Clean hook and loop pads to extend the life of hook and loop sanding discs. Practical steps, tools, and habits for smoother, longer‑lasting sanding.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="extend-life-of-hook-and-loop-sanding-discs-and-pads"&gt;Extend Life of Hook and Loop Sanding Discs and Pads&lt;/h2&gt;
